Cathars, go to their castles,

00:32:02.260 --> 00:32:05.380 align:middle line:84%
feel the vibration of
these incredible places.

00:32:05.380 --> 00:32:08.500 align:middle line:84%
We can go to Lourdes
and bathe in the waters,

00:32:08.500 --> 00:32:11.380 align:middle line:84%
